Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海啸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，抓住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是……?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们前往艾尔大陆的途中碰到了海啸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到哪里去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快醒醒啊 雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些云
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些云…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空布满了邪云的漩涡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是艾尔大陆…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『拉克尔赫普』呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都去哪里了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会发生这种事情的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩，你冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们全都死了…..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『拉克尔赫普』也沉入海底了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来什么都完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没有那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定都还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你凭什么说他们还活着?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连我们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有『拉克尔赫普』也没有办法对付魔石索沙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时世上的人全都会死在魔物的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界一定会毁灭…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时我们也会死…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去…去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是去找蕾娜他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是白费力气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会跟你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要找的话，你自己去找好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走在我前面干嘛啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想到去哪里找他们了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想先到海岸线去找一找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们既然被冲到了艾尔大陆上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜他们一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德，你真的这么想吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得逃出那个大海啸的，除了我们两个之外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再有别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非有奇迹…才有可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放弃希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它又过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲起来 雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里怎么到处都是…魔物啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是艾尔大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔石索沙就是在这里坠落的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那个海啸一定也是受到了魔石索沙的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能为了保护同伴而战…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也是为了你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却没能保护好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…妈妈…我好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看下面，马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你啰唆，也不要命令我!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定他们就在村子里面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎都荒废了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有看到什么人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁在里面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德，怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来，雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都是魔物…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是这些家伙干的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为村子里面的人报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空破斩!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑，雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想要找吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么找都没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜他们一定都还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是坚强呢 克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就不坚强…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在硬撑罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承认我不够坚强…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样的我在这个星球上认识的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我逐渐有了勇气和希望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞丽奴…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小长，小圆..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉西丝…还有蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才会想再见到他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钓到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我钓到一条很难吃的鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也抓到了只难看的螃蟹耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们就有足够的东西填饱肚皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真不是我自己夸自己呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这种艰困的环境生存的能力还真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是老大…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个拉克尔赫普现在不见了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到世界灭亡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们迟早也会变成魔物的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准说这种不吉利的话!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…也许真的会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤已经好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这样看来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你马上又能飞上天了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想飞到天上吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:13:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油…千万别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能飞的，一定能飞起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要相信你还能够飞上天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力的拍打翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一定会飞上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你飞得不错喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要相信并且一直努力希望就会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不对，克劳德?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能够放弃希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…她一定还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定能够再见到大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是攻击村子的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来…那些魔物全是这个家伙生出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?牠们要去哪里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是想要横渡大海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快饿死了，老大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊，我现在好想吃牛排哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少作梦了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有被魔物吃掉，就已经很幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么?不想活啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出现啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，被牠给逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德，快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁牠出来之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要在这里打倒牠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要找大家吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是现在你就死在这个地方的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果不将牠打倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,势必还有无数的人死在牠繁殖的那些魔物的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括拉克尔…甚至是其它大陆上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿  会从哪儿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算一瞬间也好…要是能阻止牠的活动…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减慢牠的速度的话….
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里等我….
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千年以来黑暗中的住民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请汝让邪恶的灵魂燃起复仇的怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将它丑陋的蠕动，化为悲愤的雷火阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?从海里?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟缓(Delay)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好有你帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是你…就喜欢乱来!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠能飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望实现了一个呢，雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都没事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些全都是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们找到了一个不得了的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修顿…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有找到任何关于他们的线索?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海岸那边只看到几片船身的破片被冲上岸…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它就没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们几个…这一次还能活下来已经算是奇迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定雷恩跟克劳德都已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜呢?她怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我都不忍心看她…这么痛苦的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜…也真可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克尔赫普…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是作梦吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然还能看到拉克尔赫普…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么重的东西竟然会被冲上岸来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能说这是奇迹了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个希望又实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做蕾娜．蓝佛德
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想逃离这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想见他
